Description :
        Collection of short stories: 1) My Unique Day Sorako joined a theater troupe entirely because of her admiration for Miki, the group's star. But is admiration really the only thing Sorako feels for her pretty brunette friend? 2) Pie (w)o Agemasho Anata ni Pie (w)o ne 3) Sawako-san to Uchuu Ryokou (A Space Voyage with Suwako-san) A woman falls for a married woman. 4) Mou Suki Nante Iwanai kara (I Won't Say I Love You Anymore)
